Description: mETHYLotest provides interactive Shiny-based pipelines for DNA
    methylation analysis. The EPIC module wraps ChAMP for Illumina 450K,
    EPICv1 and EPICv2 arrays with automated QC, normalisation, cell-type
    correction, batch correction, DMP/DMR detection, signature validation
    (SVM/PCA/Silhouette) and HTML reporting. The WGBS/Long-Read module wraps
    methylKit for bisulfite and nanopore/PacBio data with iterative QC,
    differential methylation, genomic annotation and multi-scenario analysis.
    An experimental episignature scoring module compares samples against
    published epigenetic signatures for genetic disorder screening.
